{"sections":[],"metadata":{"modules":[{"name":"MapLibre"}],"title":"MLNTextWritingModeHorizontal","role":"symbol","navigatorTitle":[{"text":"MLNTextWritingModeHorizontal","kind":"identifier"}],"externalID":"c:@E@MLNTextWritingMode@MLNTextWritingModeHorizontal","symbolKind":"case","roleHeading":"Enumeration Case","fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"MLNTextWritingModeHorizontal"}]},"schemaVersion":{"major":0,"minor":3,"patch":0},"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"tokens":[{"text":"MLNTextWritingModeHorizontal","kind":"identifier"}],"platforms":["iOS"],"languages":["occ"]}]},{"content":[{"anchor":"discussion","level":2,"text":"Discussion","type":"heading"},{"syntax":null,"type":"codeListing","code":[" If a text's language supports horizontal writing mode, symbols with point"," placement would be laid out horizontally."]}],"kind":"content"}],"variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlntextwritingmode\/mlntextwritingmodehorizontal"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"occ"}]}],"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre","doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNTextWritingMode"]]},"identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"occ","url":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNTextWritingMode\/MLNTextWritingModeHorizontal"},"kind":"symbol","references":{"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNTextWritingMode/MLNTextWritingModeHorizontal":{"kind":"symbol","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNTextWritingMode\/MLNTextWritingModeHorizontal","fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"MLNTextWritingModeHorizontal"}],"title":"MLNTextWritingModeHorizontal","abstract":[],"url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlntextwritingmode\/mlntextwritingmodehorizontal","role":"symbol","type":"topic"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre":{"kind":"symbol","type":"topic","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Powerful, free and open-source mapping toolkit with full control over data sources and styling."}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre","title":"MapLibre","role":"collection"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNTextWritingMode":{"type":"topic","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNTextWritingMode","title":"MLNTextWritingMode","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlntextwritingmode","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"The property allows control over a symbol’s orientation. Note that the property"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"values act as a hint, so that a symbol whose language doesn’t support the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"provided orientation will be laid out in its natural orientation. Example:"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"English point symbol will be rendered horizontally even if array value contains"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"single ‘vertical’ enum value. The order of elements in an array define priority"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"order for the placement of an orientation variant."}],"fragments":[{"text":"MLNTextWritingMode","kind":"identifier"}],"kind":"symbol","role":"symbol"}}}